   <h2 class="Entry"><div class="title_link"><a href="http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1860/mini-italia-countryman-launch">Mini Italia Countryman Launch</a></div></h2>
   <span class="Small">January 7 2011<br /></span>
   <div class="Content">
   <p><img width="680" height="380" alt="" src="http://www.thecoolhunter.com.au/images/MINICINEMA(1).jpg" /></p>
<p>TCH <a target="_blank" href="http://www.access-agency.net">ACCESS agency's</a>  collaboration with the world's best brands and ad agencies continues.  We are working on a number of fun projects with car brands, property  developers, sports brands beverage (alcohol and non) brands, movie studios.<br />
<br />
Last fall, BMW's event agency, <a href="http://www.eventswithtaste.it/" target="_blank">EWT </a>invited ACCESS to create the Mini <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thecoolhunter.net/article/detail/1749/indoor-drivein-experience-by-the-cool-hunteraccess-agency">Indoor Drive In Cinema</a> for the  launch week of Mini Countryman to the Italian media. We also created a  video presentation about the World of Innovation for the same event.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.thecoolhunter.net/images/m(1).jpg" alt="" /><br />
<br />
Since we first featured the drive-in cinema and the<a href="http://www.thecoolhunter.net/article/detail/1607/the-cool-hunter-car-wraps-coming-soon" target="_blank"> Mini car-wraps</a>, we  have been asked by numerous Mini dealers around the globe to create them  for their showrooms. So, this year, we will be creating many more  exciting and innovative Mini experiences in various international  markets. Stay tuned - <em>Bill Tikos</em></p> 
   </div>
