			<a href="http://del.icio.us/post?v=4&amp;noui&amp;jump=close&amp;url=http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1387/the-chanel-experience%2F&amp;title=thecoolhunter-Stay+Connected" class="EntryToolsDelicious" target="_blank">Del.icio.us</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1387/the-chanel-experience&t=The Chanel Experience " target="_blank" class="EntryToolsFacebook">Facebook</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://twitter.com/home?status=http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1387/the-chanel-experience%2F" target="_blank" class="EntryToolsTwitter">Twitter</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://digg.com/submit?url=http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1387/the-chanel-experience" target="_blank" class="EntryToolsDigg">Digg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.stumbleupon.com/newurl.php?url=http://www.thecoolhunter.co.uk/article/detail/1387/the-chanel-experience%2F&rating=1" target="_blank" class="EntryToolsStumble">StumbleUpon</a><br />
